{
  "_comment": "2AIO auto-delegate detector. When a user prompt looks like a substantial IMPLEMENTATION task, the codex-advisor hook injects a strong directive telling the assistant to delegate the coding to Codex (Terra/Luna) instead of hand-writing it. Tune entirely in this file (JP+EN). Fires when >=1 implement keyword matches, no exclude keyword matches, and length >= min_len.",
